B.af0=new A.c('Suppose White plays something elsewhere, how would you as Black play next? +Px1a? That wouldn\'t be a bad idea, but there is an even better move. +P-2b and then +Px2c will be more devastating to the opponent. This line of moves is what we call "authentic line"')
