B.af4=new A.c("Look at Diagram 1-2 (last move P*4i). Here you see a Pawn-anchored Silver. In this case White can drop a Pawn on 3h, so it may not seem as solid as a Pawn-anchored Gold. Still, White will need to play Px3i+ and +P-3h in order to get the promoted Rook's path open. In the meantime, you can play some effective moves.")
