B.alw=new A.c("Even if White plays K-3a in the hopes of running away to a safe place, it will be of no avail. Since White has nothing in hand other than a Pawn, he/she cannot escape from R-1a+, checkmate.")
B.aeK=new A.c("When you build up a strategy using a Rook and a smaller piece, you usually place the smaller piece ahead of the Rook for a breakthrough, but when you have a Lance in hand, the Rook can go first.")
