B.aej=new A.c("You start with exchanging Pawns on the 3rd file, then play S-3g, and then S-3f so that you can next play N3g and B-4f, which will be an ideal position on your part. Not only is there no ill-positioned Silver in front of your Pawn, but all your pieces are prepared to attack.")
