B.aeq=new A.c("Now that you get to the above position (Diagram 4), you can safely follow your instincts and play the natural moves like P-4f and N-3g. Then the position will take care of itself.")
B.afX=new A.c("Diagram 5 shows where Black is about to play deftly from the fifth-file vanguard Pawn opening. Pay attention to the right Silver.")
