B.ajx=new A.c("Black played G-3i, anticipating a Rook exchange. Then he moved the Gold onto 4i, thereby strengthening his defense. There followed a flamboyant show of exchanging both Rooks and Bishops (Diagram 2). The position is well-balanced, but take note that Black's camp allows no space for a Rook drop.")
