B.aeV=new A.c("Below is another example in which the maxim in question was put to good use. Unlike above, this is a joseki position in the central Rook against static Rook opening.")
B.Ne=new A.p("ln3g1nl/2r1gskb1/p3sp1p1/2ppp1p1p/1p7/2PPPP2P/PPBS2PP1/2G1R1SK1/LN3G1NL b -","Diagram 3")
