B.ahv=new A.c("The series of moves above leaves White's camp in a complete mess with most of the pieces disconnected with each other, while Black has at least two possibilities to play: S*5c and R6f. Either looks good.")
B.ag3=new A.c("Diagram 3 clearly shows Black is dominant at this point.")
