B.aea=new A.c("Begin with the edge-wing attack: P1e, Px1e, P*1c. This is one of the basics. When beginning the edge attack, it is crucial whether you have a Pawn in hand or not.")
B.Tb=A.a(s(["Lx1c","S*1b"]),t.s)
B.aaw=new A.Q("Moves from Diagram 2-2:",B.Tb,B.u)
B.amD=new A.c("If White neglects responding to your P*1c, you can play Lx1e.")
