B.af2=new A.c("There is nothing to hinder Black's Silver to advance to 2e, from where he can next play Sx3d thereby making the breakthrough in the 2nd file possible.")
B.al6=new A.c("If White plays G3c to secure the Pawn on 3d, Black can drop his Pawn on 2d (Diagram 3-3). Quite successful position for Black.")
