B.aib=new A.c("From Diagram 3, \n(a) if White plays Px2d, Sx2d, Gx2d, Rx2d, \n(b) if White makes no response in this area,\n   (b1) Px2c+, Gx2c, S2d, Gx2d, Rx2d, or \n   (b2) Sx3d, Gx3d, Px2c+, or \n   (b3) Sx3d, Gx2d, Sx2c+, Gx2c, Rx2c+.")
