B.ahj=new A.c("Since he cannot move the Silver from 6b, White will have a hard time coming up with an effective plan hereafter. If he plays S6c, Black can play the P4e through B*7a line. If White plays R8a, B*7b will do. Whichever way White may take, he is already on a bumpy road.")
B.WU=A.a(s([B.an6,B.Pa,B.aaq,B.NH,B.ahs,B.alE,B.a8C,B.Mv,B.ahj]),t.A)
