B.ahh=new A.c("A dangling Pawn on 8d is what you should remember when playing against the anaguma. If you capture any other piece than a Pawn, you can drop it on 8c. Diagram 2-3 shows Black has just dropped a Knight on 8c.")
B.Og=new A.p("kng1+R4/lsg6/pNppp4/1P7/PpP6/2SPP4/2BG5/1KG6/LN7 w 2p","Diagram 2-3")
