B.agY=new A.c("Before you go about recapturing a square, you need to deploy your pieces so that the square in question will be duly covered. In this case, R2f is the first step. Then you join a Pawn on 5g, thereby moving up your Silver to the crucial spot. Thus, a joining Pawn tesuji helps recapture the square which was taken by the opponent.")
