B.ama=new A.c("Prior to the above diagram, Black played P2d, after which White responded with Px2d. If Black goes on to play Sx2d, the 2nd file may seem certain to be broken into. But it is not quite so. White can then play P*2b. Then there will follow: P*2c, S3a!, Px2b+, Sx2b (Diagram 2-2).")
