B.aoR=new A.bf(48,B.ew,"Take two for one, even if there is a Pawn in it.","Nimai-gae nara Fu tomo seyo",B.a4e)
B.aen=new A.c("If someone asked me if this is literally true, I would have to answer that you'd have to take it with a grain of salt. But in shogi, just one move can be crucial meaning, so I would like to say that if you gain one move's advantage, it should be sufficient.")
B.akL=new A.c("This proverb is most often taken as an adage about the endgame, but it can be applicable in the beginning game.")
